Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.31,0:36:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最远的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At their farthest,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.43,0:36:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们之间比太阳到海王星的距离远20%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're 20% more distant than the sun is from Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.84,0:36:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们和太阳一样都有适居带\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each has a habitable zone similar to the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.81,0:36:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那也许有孕育着生命的星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where life-bearing planets could exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.77,0:36:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是人们梦寐以求的天文学圣杯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that, after all, is a holy grail in astronomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.75,0:36:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在生命周期以内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, a trip to the nearest stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.48,0:36:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去最近的星球旅行一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for example, Alpha Centauri,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.48,0:37:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如  半人马座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we can do within our lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.96,0:37:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无疑会令人激动不已\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be immensely exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.99,0:37:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学最重要的任务之一就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the great goals of science is to find life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.31,0:37:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙的其它角落发现生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}elsewhere in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.11,0:37:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跨出第一步  除了我们的太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What better place to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.71,0:37:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哪能比离我们最近的星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}other than our solar system,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.19,0:37:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加合适呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the nearest star?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.27,0:37:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在太空旅行变成了时间旅行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But now space travel becomes time travel
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.97,0:37:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望通过已知的物理定理\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as we set our sights on a mission that can be done
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.89,0:37:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来解决这个难题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}under the laws of physics we now know:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在45天内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a mission that can cross
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行驶4光年以上的距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more than 4 light-years of space in just 45 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解开时间的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our quest to unravel the mysteries of time
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.11,0:37:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又回到了太阳最近的邻居\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}now point us again to Alpha Centauri,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.97,0:37:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半人马座上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the sun's closest neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.13,0:37:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它最有可能成为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It is the most likely
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.27,0:37:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球星际飞船的第一个目的地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}first destination for a starship from earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.76,0:37:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船的这趟航行就是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a starship whose mission cannot avoid
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.01,0:38:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次完整的时空旅行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a component of time travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.57,0:38:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不清楚通过怎样的技术手段\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have no idea what kind of technology
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我们往返于半人马座和地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would actually take us from here to Alpha Centauri and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.15,0:38:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}肖恩·卡洛尔\N加州理工学院
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.86,0:38:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们能以光速的99.99%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and say that we just move at 99.99% the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.71,0:38:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路飞过去再一路飞回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the way there and then all the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.53,0:38:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于要做这种长距离航行的飞船来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ship seems surprisingly small
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.52,0:38:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太小了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for one that has to make such a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.02,0:38:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在航行期间  它如何向乘员提供充足的供给\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How can it hold enough supplies to support a crew for the duration?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.25,0:38:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没问题  因为它不仅仅是艘星际飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It can, because it is not only a starship,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.86,0:38:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是台时光机器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is also a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行要花费8.6年的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would take about 8.6 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.07,0:38:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为半人马座距离我们4.3光年远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because Alpha Centauri is 4.3 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.40,0:38:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于飞船上的人来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But to the people on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.11,0:38:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用了不到两个月的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would take less than two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约只要45天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would take about 45 days
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.10,0:38:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们在以接近光速的速度航行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they're traveling close to the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.33,0:38:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了迅速达到接近光速的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The astronauts would also have to overcome the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员必须克服致命的加速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of killer acceleration in quickly reaching the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.78,0:38:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则  只能缓慢的加速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otherwise, they'd have to speed up slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.72,0:39:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大大增加了航行时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}adding time to the total trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.95,0:39:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于想为星际旅行寻找港口的地球人来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Alpha Centauri is the go-to destination for earthbound beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.96,0:39:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半人马座是个令人向往的目的地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hoping for a toehold in star travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.41,0:39:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝非偶然的是 在詹姆斯·卡梅隆的电影阿凡达中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's no accident that James Cameron chose it as home
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.13,0:39:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚构的星球潘多拉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to his fictional moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.82,0:39:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被设置成半人马座星系中的一颗卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pandora, in the movie Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.51,0:39:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之所以要飞往半人马座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The reason we would go to Alpha Centauri has to do with today's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.12,0:39:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与现在望远镜围绕半人马座B星进行的大量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}intensive telescope search for earth-like planets
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.02,0:39:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类地行星搜寻不无关系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}around Alpha Centauri "B"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.12,0:39:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是半人马座系统中主双星之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of two stars in the system's main binary pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.91,0:39:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止  要在整片天空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Alpha Centauri "B" it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.65,0:39:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找小质量类地行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is by far the best star in the entire sky
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.97,0:39:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}格雷戈·朗丁\N加州大学圣克鲁兹分校
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.90,0:39:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半人马座B星是最好的目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for searching for low-mass, earth-like planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.72,0:39:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要完成这种搜寻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But to carry out that kind of search requires
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.30,0:39:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要付出巨大的努力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a very dedicated effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.98,0:39:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是你用望远镜观察几个晚上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's not something that you can accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.54,0:39:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能完成的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a few nights with a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.41,0:40:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想从一张航天照片中区分半人马座的两颗主星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's hard enough to separate the two main stars
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.01,0:40:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分困难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of Alpha Centauri in a space photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.15,0:40:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而想在两颗星中一颗的周围寻找一颗地球大小的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Trying to see an earth-size planet around one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.06,0:40:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在来看  是不可能的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is, at the moment, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.19,0:40:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找到这种星球  最好的机会是摆动侦测法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The best shot we have is to find the planet by the wobble method,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.50,0:40:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能侦测出由每颗星球自身微小的引力而引起的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}detecting a star's subtle back-and-forth motion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.24,0:40:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星体细微的往复摆动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}caused by the tiny gravitational tug any planet would have on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.88,0:40:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与时间旅行一样  这几乎是不可能的任务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like time travel, it seems almost undoable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.54,0:40:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想侦测的这种往复摆动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The back-and-forth wobble,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当相当的细微\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we need to detect is incredibly small.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.92,0:40:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在玫瑰碗球场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm here at the Rose Bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.00,0:40:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把半人马座的大小比作这座球场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and if the Rose Bowl were the size of Alpha Centauri,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.12,0:40:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们需要侦测的摆动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then the amount of wobble
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.92,0:40:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we need to detect is about this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.05,0:40:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.3英寸大  而且还是从\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about 3.3 inches, and we need to detect that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.23,0:40:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四百三十万英里外侦测这么点大小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from 4.3 million miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.41,0:41:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半人马座B星比A稍微小一点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Alpha Centauri "B" is slightly smaller than "A"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.99,0:41:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦测行星的行动也集中在那\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the planet hunt is concentrated there,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.46,0:41:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是因为较小的星球会表现出更多的摆动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}mostly because a smaller star will show more wobble
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.89,0:41:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让侦测轻松许多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and detection will be that much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.54,0:41:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三到五年内  真相应该就能揭晓了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In three to five years, we should have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.87,0:41:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果将来我们发现了一颗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think that if we were to discover that there's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.53,0:41:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球质量级的星球围绕着最靠近恒星运动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an earth-mass planet orbiting the very nearest star,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将会是一件激动人心的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then there would be a great deal of excitement to somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.22,0:41:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们会设法建立大型望远镜观测它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}either build a large telescope to try to observe that planet
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.04,0:41:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或在遥远的未来酝酿出一个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or perhaps in the far future to design a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.56,0:41:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造访它的计划\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that could actually go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.50,0:41:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试时间旅行的目标明确以后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With the goal of our time travel quest identified,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.29,0:41:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以想象  地球轨道上的宇宙飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can imagine our spacecraft in earth orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会飞往它们的第一个任务目标  半人马座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about to leave on the first mission to Alpha Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.53,0:41:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高的速度让飞船成了时光机器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ship's high speed propels it into time machine mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.30,0:42:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的时钟变慢  因此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}slowing its clock, so its passengers approach
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.98,0:42:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客在三或四周内就能抵达半人马座\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Alpha Centauri in three or four weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.78,0:42:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还能近距离欣赏到人类从未见过的景象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}seeing things up close no human has ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.97,0:42:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先看到的是人马座的比邻红矮星的耀斑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}First up, a stellar flare from the red dwarf, Proxima Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它处在三星系统的外围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On the outskirts of the triple system,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.79,0:42:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三颗星中离太阳最近的一颗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is the closest of the three to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人马座的比邻星经常发生突然的喷发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Proxima Centauri is prone to these sudden outbursts
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.02,0:42:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使得它在一天的时间里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that can cause it to brighten up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.34,0:42:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能突然变亮四五次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by a factor of four or five over the course of just a day
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.87,0:42:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又迅速黯淡下来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then fade back just as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.78,0:42:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  当你们经过半人马座比邻星时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you might be in for some real fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.29,0:42:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可能处在真正的"烟花"中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as you pass by Proxima Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.90,0:42:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}艾力克斯·菲利潘科\N加州大学伯克利分校
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.82,0:42:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以设想  飞船能绕过半人马座A星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we might imagine swinging past Alpha Centauri "A"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.62,0:42:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并在引力的帮助下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and using gravity assist
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.50,0:42:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝半人马座B星方向驶去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to send us in a direction of Alpha Centauri "B".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.89,0:42:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行的终点是地球的姐妹星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The sister earth at the ship's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.15,0:42:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我们的最终目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the ultimate goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.05,0:43:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者们急于探索它  希冀发现上面的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the travelers will be anxious to explore it and search for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.99,0:43:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管旅行者们的旅途只花了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although the trip has taken
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.33,0:43:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个多月的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}little more than a few months for the travelers,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.01,0:43:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是超高的速度大大减慢了他们的时钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the high speed will slow down their clocks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.45,0:43:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着  当他们返回时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so much, that when they return,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上已经流逝了将近十年的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}nearly a decade will have passed on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.49,0:43:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现高速星际旅行的梦想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The realization of star travel at high speed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.33,0:43:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能留给遥远的未来去实现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a dream for the far future.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.21,0:43:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个技术先进  发展迅速的世界里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On an earth where technology is so advanced and changing so fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.48,0:43:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八或十年的时间里  足以发生戏剧性的变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the difference of 8 or 10 years could be dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.93,0:43:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时时空旅行也许会成为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This kind of time travel may become routine
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.41,0:43:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一代星际旅行者的家常便饭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to a new generation of star travelers...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.69,0:43:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类也将在探索宇宙这一壮阔的旅途中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Taking mankind on the next giant leap
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.10,0:43:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下一个伟大的目标进发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in its epic journey through The Universe.
